{"tid":2217558,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"英國公共部門借款急升，再創新高","createTime":"2020-09-25T13:56:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-27T16:29:21.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"d5191aa0ae01259e34972730b39a4cb55ebfad5f","tid":2217558,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T13:56:01.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1551684-20200925.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1551684-20200925.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=awVbgeYyyy76%2F43Y8QfwznO%2BoULzyGumsBrFMfYiBSk%3D&h=37b95ceb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1551684-20200925.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=4b48536e\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1551684-20200925.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n英國公共部門借款8月再次飆升至紀錄高位，由巨額抗疫支出所致。<br />\n<br />\n扣除國有銀行的公共部門淨借款急升至359億英鎊，低於市場預期的380億英鎊，但按月增長1.3倍。<br />\n<br />\n今個財政年度以來，政府在5個月內已借入1737億英鎊，超越了截至2010年3月止的財政年度創下的1577億英鎊紀錄。<br />\n<br />\n政府預算，今個年度結束時，赤字或高達3720億英鎊，借款與國內生產總值(GDP)比例將提高至18.9%，將是二戰以來最高比例，並遠高於長期可持續水平。<br />\n<br />\n另外，8月公共部門淨債務達到2.024萬億英鎊，相當於GDP的101.9%，是1960-61財政年度以來最高水平。"},{"pid":"8bdc51371234fc1661483cec3009164a118e0dfd","tid":2217558,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T14:07:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>另外，8月公共部門淨債務達到2.024萬億英鎊，相當於GDP的101.9%，是1960-61財政年度以來最高水平。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n好驚英國會頂唔住 <br />\n<br />\n依家開始入冬, 狂爆肺炎同冬季流感 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c40c69499f46c6f16e20a4e653bb06d3035c6f34","tid":2217558,"uid":152705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8bdc51371234fc1661483cec3009164a118e0dfd","tid":2217558,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-25T14:07:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>另外，8月公共部門淨債務達到2.024萬億英鎊，相當於GDP的101.9%，是1960-61財政年度以來最高水平。</